" Ctrl+Up/Down/j/k to move across display lines (i.e., including line breaks)
nnoremap <C-Up> gk
inoremap <C-Up> <C-O>gk
vnoremap <C-Up> gk
nnoremap <C-Down> gj
inoremap <C-Down> <C-O>gj
vnoremap <C-Down> gj
nnoremap <C-k> gk
vnoremap <C-k> gk
nnoremap <C-j> gj
vnoremap <C-j> gj

