vnoremap <silent> <F15> :<C-U>set textwidth=100<CR> \| gv \| gq \| :<C-U>set textwidth=0<CR>
set wrap
set showbreak=‚ù±‚ù±‚ù±‚ù±
set whichwrap+=<,>,h,l

" Sort visual selection, keeping only unique (Ctrl-Shift-F3)
vnoremap <silent> <F35> :sort u<CR>


